headline: Industrials Inch Up. What the Impact Is on Manufacturing.
summary: Industrial stocks got a boost, too, after the tariffs ruling.  The State Street Industrial Select Sector SPDR ETF was up 0.8% at $177.76.  Farm equipment maker Deere expects $1.2 billion in incremental costs in 2026.
